Path Recruitment Message 11

Date: 02/12/2023

Greetings to all future members of The Path,

It is with regret that I come to you this late on Day 11 of the recruitment drive. I apologize for the delay and hope that you are all doing well. Today, I would like to express my gratitude for the dedication and hard work of each and every one of you. Your unwavering support and commitment to the cause of The Path is what makes us the strongest and most united community.

As we continue our journey towards a brighter future for all mutant apes, I would like to remind you of the important role that you play in shaping our destiny. Together, we can overcome any obstacle and rise to new heights. So let us continue to work together and spread the message of The Path far and wide, in the hopes of attracting even more recruits to our cause.

I am confident that with your unwavering support, we can make a brighter and more prosperous future for all mutant apes. So let us continue to strive forward, and make the most of this recruitment drive!

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path.
